Small test program I wrote to test my growl library (http://github.com/kfdm/gntp/)
Queries AnimeNFO (http://www.animenfo.com/radio/) and sends a growl message

Usage: radio.py [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -H HOST, --hostname=HOST
  -p PORT, --port=PORT  port to send on
  -P PASSWORD, --password=PASSWORD
                        network password
  -a APP, --appname=APP
  -t TITLE, --title=TITLE
  -d, --debug           Print raw growl packets
